components:
  securitySchemes:
    OAuth2:
      type: oauth2
      flows:
        client_credentials:
          authorizationUrl: https://api.example.com/oauth2/authorize
          tokenUrl: https://api.example.com/oauth2/token
          scopes:
            api: All API access
  schemas:
    Merchant:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 255
        business_type:
          type: string
          enum: [retail, ecommerce, saas, subscription, marketplace, other]
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [active, inactive, suspended]
        created_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        updated_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - business_type
        - status
        - created_at
        - updated_at
    MerchantCreateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 255
          example: "Acme Corporation"
        business_type:
          type: string
          enum: [retail, ecommerce, saas, subscription, marketplace, other]
          example: "ecommerce"
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [active, inactive, suspended]
          default: "active"
      required:
        - name
        - business_type
    MerchantUpdateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
          maxLength: 255
        business_type:
          type: string
          enum: [retail, ecommerce, saas, subscription, marketplace, other]
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [active, inactive, suspended]
    MerchantListResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Merchant'
        pagination:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pagination'
    Payment:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        merchant_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          minimum: 0
        currency:
          type: string
          pattern: '^[A-Z]{3}$'
          example: "USD"
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [pending, processing, completed, failed, refunded]
        created_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        updated_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        failure_reason:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        metadata:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
          nullable: true
      required:
        - id
        - merchant_id
        - amount
        - currency
        - status
        - created_at
        - updated_at
    PaymentCreateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          minimum: 0.01
          example: 99.99
        currency:
          type: string
          pattern: '^[A-Z]{3}$'
          example: "USD"
        metadata:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
          nullable: true
          description: Optional metadata for the payment
      required:
        - amount
        - currency
    PaymentCreatedResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [pending]
        message:
          type: string
          example: "Payment processed successfully"
        next_action:
          type: object
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              example: "check_status"
            url:
              type: string
              format: uri
              example: "/v1/payments/{payment_id}"
    PaymentListResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        data:
          type: array

          format: uuid
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          minimum: 0
        reason:
          type: string
          maxLength: 500
          nullable: true
        status:
          type: string
          enum: [pending, processing, completed, failed]
        created_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        updated_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
      required:
        - id
        - payment_id
        - amount
        - status
        - created_at
        - updated_at
    RefundCreateRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        amount:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          minimum: 0.01
          example: 49.99
        reason:
          type: string
